  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://ollama.com/assets/library/nemotron-mini/4e0ea563-a507-45e7-ad0b-b083918ec11b\" width=\"320\"/></p>\n\n<p>Nemotron-Mini-4B-Instruct is a model for generating responses for roleplaying, retrieval augmented generation, and function calling. It is a small language model (SLM) optimized through distillation, pruning and quantization for speed and on-device deployment.</p>\n\n<p>This instruct model is optimized for roleplay, RAG QA, and function calling in English. It supports a context length of 4,096 tokens. This model is ready for commercial use.</p>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://blogs.nvidia.com/blog/digital-human-technology-mecha-break/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blog</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/nvidia/Nemotron-Mini-4B-Instruct\" rel=\"nofollow\">HuggingFace</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
